text: Novonikolayevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Kacheganovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 13 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 5 km from Kacheganovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Novonikolayevka, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
